4"><svg/></span></button></div><a tabindex="0" class="e2604eec _8a34cedd _03790f26 fa08621d _2dbaefe9 _6c4d11e3 ba894f4c _00e78148 def9e035 e070083c" href="https://www.linkedin.com/feed/update/urn:li:activity:7414274158265716736/" componentkey="feed-commentary_60274b50-57bf-4661-bbd2-c32bdbf47495"><p class="aaa2a34c a0b37d66 b5859774 _3d331bbe _132a85bf _36d77b6f edb0fe3a _38c8bff9 _8533cd3e _96ed007d _580de4b6 _7e00b75a _83931314 bf19327c _9e30f760" componentkey="feed-commentary_60274b50-57bf-4661-bbd2-c32bdbf47495"><span class="_8f2f94ab _8461674f ddd9785f _1ff3de1f c30b9f65 b191f414 _5e4b880e d1d3c94b" tabindex="-1" data-testid="expandable-text-box">The one feature I missed the most is finally here. 🔔<br/><br/>When I first launched ListLao, the sync was fast. If you had the app open, you saw items appear instantly.<br/><br/>But there was a flaw in my own design.<br/><br/>My wife would add items to our list while I was driving to the store. Since I wasn't looking at the app, I had no idea the list had changed. I’d walk in, buy the milk, and realize later I missed the eggs she added 10 minutes ago.<br/><br/>Passively syncing wasn't enough. The app needed to speak up.<br/>So today, I’m rolling out Instant Notifications.<br/><br/>Now, the moment someone collaborates on your list, you get notified. It turns the app from a static list into a live, active conversation. And yes, we managed to do this without requiring you to sign up or give us your email.<br/><br/>It was a tricky engineering challenge to keep it "login-free" while handling push notifications, but it’s working beautifully.<br/><br/>Check out the update and let me know if the alerts are fast enough for you! 👇<br/><br/><a class="_00e78148 ce10ced0" href="https://www.linkedin.com/search/results/all/?keywords=%23indiedev&amp;origin=HASH_TAG_FROM_FEED" tabindex="-1"><span class="_03b827d3"><strong>#IndieDev</strong></span></a><span class="f717e234"></span><a class="_00e78148 ce10ced0" href="https://www.linkedin.com/search/results/all/?keywords=%23androiddev&amp;origin=HASH_TAG_FROM_FEED" tabindex="-1"><span class="_03b827d3"><strong>#AndroidDev</strong></span></a><span class="f717e234"></span><a class="_00e78148 ce10ced0" href="https://www.linkedin.com/search/results/all/?keywords=%23featureupdate&amp;origin=HASH_TAG_FROM_FEED" tabindex="-1"><span class="_03b827d3"><strong>#FeatureUpdate</strong></span></a><span class="f717e234"></span><a class="_00e78148 ce10ced0" href="https://www.linkedin.com/search/results/all/?keywords=%23pushnotifications&amp;origin=HASH_TAG_FROM_FEED" tabindex="-1"><span class="_03b827d3"><strong>#PushNotifications</strong></span></a><span class="f717e234"></span><a class="_00e78148 ce10ced0" href="https://www.linkedin.com/search/results/all/?keywords=%23listlao&amp;origin=HASH_TAG_FROM_FEED" tabindex="-1"><span class="_03b827d3"><strong>#ListLao</strong></span></a><span class="f717e234"></span><a class="_00e78148 ce10ced0" href="https://www.linkedin.com/search/results/all/?keywords=%23buildinpublic&amp;origin=HASH_TAG_FROM_FEED" tabindex="-1"><span class="_03b827d3"><strong>#BuildInPublic</strong></span></a><button class="_6a92e007 _2759ecc5 ee71e134 _94a1a0a8 _80e4dbd7 _9f89ee13 fa7cc803 bc833b0a _4589e26e _3eb6b839 ba894f4c dd149073 _416320e0 _22e9397a _71bd1774" type="button" aria-hidden="true" data-testid="expandable-text-button"><span><span><span class="_83931314">…</span><span>more</span></span></span></button></span></p></a><div class="_97fb1bf8 b191f414 _251d36ac _051e6a8d"><a tabindex="0" class="_251d36ac _27e8dda2 ab52c0ec e2604eec _8a34cedd _03790f26 fa08621d _2dbaefe9 _6c4d11e3 ba894f4c _00e78148 def9e035 e070083c" href="https://www.linkedin.com/feed/update/urn:li:activity:7414274158265716736/" componentkey="42738aab-d19a-4e66-aae1-b38f24bc0150"><figure class="c9b0261d b5859774 _1ff3de1f _1fb58c8f _3eb6b839" componentkey="42738aab-d19a-4e66-aae1-b38f24bc0150" data-color-scheme="dark"><img class="_0ca109ea _13294e96 ebc5971b _1fb58c8f 